  <name>Terma</name>
  <summary>Modern terminal emulator with split panes, tabs and AI agent support</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Terma is a modern terminal emulator built with Electron, React and xterm.js.
      It features split panes with unlimited nesting, multiple tabs with color coding,
      and a rich set of integrated tools — all in a single window.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>6 pane types: terminal, file manager, AI agent, markdown viewer, image viewer, system monitor</li>
      <li>Split panes with unlimited nesting and drag-and-drop rearrangement</li>
      <li>Multiple tabs with color coding</li>
      <li>Git integration and SSH file browsing</li>
      <li>Voice input via Whisper and TTS via ElevenLabs</li>
      <li>4 built-in color themes</li>
      <li>Session persistence</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

